# 💼 Project 3 — Microsoft 365 AI Workflow

Worked on a concept for connecting Microsoft 365 tools into a unified project reporting system.

## Goal

Move from manual status reporting to automated executive visibility using tools we already own.

---

## Proposed Workflow

```text
Microsoft Forms
        │
        ▼
SharePoint List
        │
        ▼
Power Automate
        │
        ▼
Copilot Executive Summary
        │
        ▼
Microsoft Teams
```

---

## Strategic Positioning

Rather than requesting new software...

Present the project as an **Operational Optimization** initiative using existing Microsoft 365 licenses.

### Benefits

- Zero additional licensing costs
- Zero procurement delays
- Zero additional security reviews
- Standardized reporting
- Automated executive summaries
- Better leadership visibility

---

## Leadership Pitch

Instead of selling technology...

Sell:

- Standardized reporting
- Reduced administrative work
- Better executive visibility
- Faster decision-making
- AI-assisted summaries

Recommended pilot:

- Teams Channel
- Microsoft Form
- SharePoint List
- Power Automate
- Copilot Executive Summary

